        <item>
            <title>Sony 全新 RGB LED 背光技術，挑戰 4000nits 峯值亮度與色彩精準度極限</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/15/sony-rgb-led/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-rgb-led</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/15/sony-rgb-led/wireless-home/audio-visual/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 15 Mar 2025 01:26:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音產品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Sony RGB LED]]>
            </category>
